fields.name: ApplicationId
fields.description: Application ID of the client making request on behalf of a principal

fields.name: ObjectId
fields.description: The object ID of a user, service principal or security group in the Azure Active Directory tenant for the vault. The object ID must be unique for the list of access policies.

fields.name: Permissions
fields.description: Permissions the identity has for keys, secrets and certificates.

fields.name: TenantId
fields.description: The Azure Active Directory tenant ID that should be used for authenticating requests to the key vault.
